727799f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 68th Drive
727799f-a.text:
Oueens Boulevard, north side, at 68th Drive, showing the John
Van Dine house. Some of the ownors were: John Van Dine 1852-1873;
J. Van Dine Estate 1873; A. Van Dine 1891; and Mrs. Van Dyne 1896.
At the extreme right is seen a part of the Ascan Backus home. View
No. 2 shows the outbuildings and a section of the house.
April 1923.
View 2: 1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
